DocAttribute.Name: ActualDate
DocAttribute.Documentation: The date on which an event actually occurs. It is a measured value.

DocAttribute.Name: EarlyDate
DocAttribute.Documentation: The earliest date on which an event can occur. It is a calculated value.

DocAttribute.Name: LateDate
DocAttribute.Documentation: The latest date on which an event can occur. It is a calculated value.

DocAttribute.Name: ScheduleDate
DocAttribute.Documentation: The date on which an event is scheduled to occur. The value might be measured or somehow calculated, which is defined by _ScheduleDataOrigin_.
